snippet.title: Limit Theory Gameplay Demo 2
snippet.description: Early prototype of the in-game ship/station editor for Limit Theory.  This was unlocked as a stretch goal for our Kickstarter campaign.  Learn more at http://LTheory.com.  Support the dream at http://kickstarter.LTheory.com !
